  <brief_title>Effectiveness and Safety of Dysport® (abobotulinumtoxinA) in Paediatric Lower Limb Spasticity</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase IV, Prospective, Observational, Multicentre Study Evaluating the Effectiveness and Safety of Dysport® (abobotulinumtoxinA) in Paediatric Lower Limb Spasticity.</official_title>
