  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the longitudinal attainment of subject centred and
      functional related goals (cumulated Goal Attainment Scale Total (GAS T) score) after
      abobotulinumtoxinA injection (including following repeated injection cycles where they occur)
      alongside spasticity management used in real life settings over a period of 18 months (and a
      maximum of six injection cycles).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
